   I was born in 1971. My father had only been back a short time from the war. I dont know where or what happened to him He left when I was three months old. What little bits I get from family and writings I've stolen from my ignorant mother lead me to believe he was emotionaly unstable.I'm trying to get over my dad leaving my older brother and I.My life has been hard,I've stopped being mad.I just feel the loss.He knows how to find me, if he wanted to.I know he may be struggling.I would have been there for him.I wish I had been daddy's girl.       
